import React from 'react'
import Navbar from '../../Components/Navbar/Navbar'
import Vocab from '../../Components/Vocab/Vocab'
import Footer from '../../Components/Footer/Footer'

const VocabHindi = () => {
  return (
    <>
        <Navbar/>
        <Vocab apiValue="/hindiVocab" />
        <Footer/>
    </>
  )
}

export default VocabHindi
